reviewText: REAL HOT SEXY BABIES... HIGHLY RECOMMANDED !!!

Comparing this to other titles from the J-Idols series, I was expecting more. The total video is only about 40~45 minutes and most of that is shots of Miho doing nothing but lying down or reading a book. Still, she's beautiful and great to look at, but this could have been better. 4 stars for a hot Japanese supermodel. Just don't expect much if you have seen other J-Idols (Fumika & Nanae are much better and are longer).

Okay, this isn't Casablanca or Gone With The Wind,  but it is a fun video. A day in the life of a cutie from Japan. Do you like Race Queens and Bikini Idols from Japan? This is the video for you! Go shopping, driving, to the beach and sun bathing with this hottie. You won't regret it!!
